narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend it if you are interested in Chinese, willing to invest the time, and want to continue learning the language:

I would definitely recommend Chinese 151 to any student interested in maintaining their Chinese abilities. Having now been away from a light summer program for over a semester, I could definitely feel my speaking abilities slipping. But that being said, I think this course does its best to maintain speaking and listening abilities while developing a vocabulary base.
I would definitely recommend the course
